parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to the deactivation of airbags, which can increase the risk of injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The airbag light illuminates or flashes
the passenger airbag light comes on
the airbag system warning light stays on
the airbag system is not functioning properly
the spiral cable needs to be replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unavailability of recall repair parts can delay the repair of safety-critical issues, increasing the risk of accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The recall repair part is not available
the manufacturer has exceeded a reasonable amount of time for the recall repair
the local dealership is unable to perform the recall repair.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission failure can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or stranding the driver.
symptoms: the transmission needs to be replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Sudden power loss or engine stalling can cause accidents or leave the driver stranded.

the front wheels turn at a faster rate than the rear wheels.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the drive shaft or transmission mounting can cause loss of control, accidents, or stranding the driver.

mechanics unable to diagnose the issue.
